# BeyondAllReason-StarwarMod
What mod does?
Turn most weapon into pew pew laser. Exaggrerated artillery.

What AI does?
AI can build scav unit. Epic Tzar, Tyrannus, Flying blackhydra etc.

Lobby configuration Must:
!bSet scavunitsforplayers 1

Lobby configuration Suggestion:
Glacial Gap
StarwarAI +100
!bSet evocom 1
!bSet evocomlevelupmethod timed
!bSet evocomleveluptime 3
!setallaibonus 100

Download the Starwar folder in this repository
Extract the folder to <Beyond-All-Reason installation path>\data\engine\recoil_<latest date>\AI\Skirmish\
The full path may look something like this:
C:\Program Files\Beyond-All-Reason\data\engine\recoil_2025.04.04\AI\Skirmish\Starwar\AI\AIInfo.lua

Tweakdef to copy paste in lobby 
!bset tweakdefs1 
!bset tweakdefs2 
!bset tweakdefs3 
!bset tweakdefs4
